{"tid":702287,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[數學白痴] 有無數神可以解答下我呢條問題","createTime":"2018-06-14T18:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T23:04:01.000Z","uid":128109,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6f83122f2d56c74a941000c276f8de7010488e75","tid":702287,"uid":128109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T18:33:47.000Z","msg":"我係數學白痴黎，有條數學問題仲係困擾左我好耐。雖然明白中間個論證過程，但仲係理解唔到個答案點解一定係0.05。<br />\n<br />\nIf a bat and a ball together cost $1.10, and the bat cost $1.00 more than the ball, how much does the ball cost?<br />\n<br />\nLet the cost of the bat = A<br />\n<br />\nLet the cost of the ball = B<br />\n<br />\nFrom the question, we have:<br />\n<br />\nA + B = $1.10<br />\nA = B + $1.00 &rarr; A - B = $1.00<br />\nAdding these equations, we have:<br />\n<br />\n2A = $2.10 &rarr; A = $1.05 &rarr; B = $0.05<br />\n<br />\nAnswer: $0.05<br />\n<br />\n咁點解個Bat 唔可以係價值1.01 跟住個ball價值0.09，咁個total 都係1.10。而個bat都係cost $1.00 more than the ball。點解個答案一定係0.05。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eeb32b9ee3c73d3a5252dc8524a09131bd0520a","tid":702287,"uid":179571,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T18:34:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"629aeb871879c34439df339055236180ec14e705","tid":702287,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eeb32b9ee3c73d3a5252dc8524a09131bd0520a","tid":702287,"uid":179571,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6f83122f2d56c74a941000c276f8de7010488e75","tid":702287,"uid":128109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT